clusterList.phrase: that is a very good move by the opposition when the talks started we said we were very skeptical about mugabe's intentions we believed that he was only asking the opposition and the opposition asking zanu-pf to come up with its lists of demands and the proposal that came from zanu-pf shows that mugabe's intention was to swallow the opposition and surely we cannot be creating vice presidents anytime there is a crisis and when there are negotiations we solve that by creating vice presidents
